data.description: This unique, larger one-of-a-kind home in the Near South neighborhood with three larger bedrooms, three bath areas, and a two-vehicle garage is ready for your review. Mostly brick exterior, covered front stoop, partially covered 28x8 patio, fenced backyard, and sunken backyard with several plantings. A long driveway for off-street parking. There is a gardening shed on the back of the garage. Note the fountain and yard statues throughout the landscape. Inside the home, the wood floors and ornate wood trim really stand out. There is also a formal dining room, wood-burning fireplace, large sunroom, and a third-floor attic area that can be used for a playroom or storage. The price has been adjusted for some maintenance items and updates. You're invited to take a look to see if this house can be the next home for you.
